node.text: I hope you get the point, these cases were built to last. Couple notes: this iPhone was from the 50 foot drops and works intermittently and screen protector was not ours. Unreal protection starting at $30! Ramping up tracking, frosted this week, Crystal/Rebel rollout will begin next week.

node.text: Flex Series is almost here! Currently finalizing the molds with texture and entering mass production next week. A late release for iPhone 12 but will have 13 models on time. This design took over a year to create and required a far more complex engineering and production process. Every detail was sculpted with intention, we hope you’ll appreciate our efforts! Will have preorders up soon 👌

node.text:
Our masterpiece is complete. Rebel Series Gen-3 will be the most beautiful case on the market, guaranteed. Improved in every way over Gen-2 design. 
- Sharper, refined styling. No case has ever had this much attention to detail.
- New, stiffer, more advanced frame construction.
- 1.35mm thinner.
- 15g lighter.
- Further shaved sides create a striking aesthetic with more holding comfort.
- New, grippier texture on sides.
- Metal buttons further improve clickiness + improved dust seal.
- Far more camera lens protection with new volcano lip design.
- Inner shock absorbers + inner microfiber sheet provide maximum durability in an incredibly thin frame.
- Of course our stronger MagSafe strength carries over from Gen-2.
- Top of the line screen protector included.

Working overtime to make launch, colors & Crystal to be announced. Frosted is coming back 😋 Stay tuned 👌

node.text: Gen-3 prototype looking sleek 🔪😍 Much thinner, lighter, less wide, more comfortable sculpting and fully sealed metal buttons will provide top notch dust resistance. The most advanced construction case for the iPhone 13 lineup, guaranteed. We are working day and night to have these ready for launch. Will have multiple colors & Crystal colors to share soon. Flex on track for next month 🚀

node.text: So grateful to be here, our third product launch. The American dream is still alive for the willing but boy is it a difficult road. Happy 4th everyone, thank you for helping us get this far. Just wanted to share my excitement for Flex series, been using for a week and it’s so so right. Comfortable, sharp and the design was well worth the year we spent on it. Will include 3 pairs of side stickers and will now be one piece. Tooling is being prepared, soon guys 😁

node.text: Our first Gen-2 sale is live! Take $5 off any Crystal or Rebel Gen-2 cases until July 4th. Use promo: “HAPPY4” at checkout! Also, Gen-2 Crystal is back in stock for 12 Pro Max! Updates soon on Flex series production 🎆

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Phone Rebel Cases on June 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and phone.

node.text: Our upcoming Flex Series pushes side-less case design to the limits. Sleeker, now symmetrical, comfort oriented, signature ‘claw’ durability & powerful MagSafe support. We took our time on sculpting for the best possible design flow on Apple’s new square iPhones. Faithful to the OG, Flex series can balance on ALL 4 sides now 😆👌 Even though these are rough CNC prototypes, we’re very happy with the outcome and are confirming final molds & production. We hope to be shipping these beauties by August. Prices to come, will be very reasonable. (Finals will not have these deep mold lines, just wanted to share our progress in prototyping 👌)

node.text: Sneak peak of our most ambitious design to date, funded by your Gen-2 purchases. Gen-3 cases will have the most advanced & unique construction out of any case out there. Going all out this year. Thinner, lighter, stronger, grippier, new colors, dust-free metal buttons & unparalleled aesthetics. We promised to get better every year, we intend to only improve. Any suggestions for new colors? Leave them below ✌️
